description: Use this UUID to get more information about a particular result, you should store for later usage as a reference.
The customer identifier used in creating this result.
Lets the user know if this was a test request.

It adds transparency on where the report is at any particular point. Expect one of the following values: 
"Queued"
"In progress"
"Processing done"
"Processing Error" 
"Webhook done"
"Webhook failed"
